  "description": "Fedor Ikelaar is back! The Dutch globetrotting comedian brings a fresh, high-energy show packed with big laughs, sharp cultural insights, and hilarious misadventures. Seen in 50+ countries, Fedor flips stereotypes and delivers an unforgettable ride of comedy, storytelling and self-reflection. Buckle up!",
